{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban MPs from accepting payments from overseas businesses.",
        "additional_details": "This campaign seeks to ban our elected representatives from accepting any type of payment, salary, contribution or gratuity, other than a reasonable level of hospitality when overseas on official business, from any individual, group, partnership, association, company or corporation domiciled outside the UK.",
        "background": "Many MPs undertake paid work or consultancy in addition to their parliamentary duties which, in some cases, pays more than their official salary. At a time when Western democracy is under unprecedented attack, we must not allow MPs to be paid by companies based overseas.",
